label: Mary Motte Alston Pringle Receipt Book
description: Receipt book belonging to Mary Motte Alston Pringle containing recipes, methods and remedies for food, housekeeping, and medicine from family, friends, articles and world travelers.  Pringle often notes on effectiveness and provides personal anecdotes.  Pages numbered 74 through 97 in Pringle's book are blank and therefore omitted.  The table of contents can be found at the end of the book.
